01:44:48,000 --> 01:44:51,000
Most of it
has been turned black through soot,

2321
01:44:51,000 --> 01:44:53,000
but the cap is perfect.
Perfect condition.

2322
01:44:53,000 --> 01:44:55,500
TALIESIN: I have a special
set of pajamas myself, so I understand.

2323
01:44:55,500 --> 01:44:57,000
MATT: "They are comfortable."

2324
01:44:57,000 --> 01:45:01,000
As he walks in,
still bandaged on the arm,

2325
01:45:01,000 --> 01:45:03,000
you can see there's

2326
01:45:03,000 --> 01:45:06,000
a small kettle of tea
