2327
01:45:06,000 --> 01:45:08,530
It's a tiny little table
and a tiny little stool

2328
01:45:08,530 --> 01:45:11,000
that he's just kind of
sitting on right there.

2329
01:45:11,000 --> 01:45:13,490
And he goes
and he reaches over for the kettle.

2330
01:45:13,490 --> 01:45:15,370
"(groans)"

